divs: Sighting Detailsseen a circle of lights in the sky that was huge. Other objects flying around the same area every night. The objects go up and down,left and right, diagonal. Sometimes the dissapear. There out there every night. We leave on a farm. There were also 4 cows in the area missing which Im not saying the objects had anything to do with the cows but just a thought. The objects sort of make my Mother and I nervous. My Mother seen the circl of lights and says it looked out of this world. Ever since we started seeing the objects that look like stars but move in all sorts of directions we look out the window alot at night. My Mother got up around 4am when she seen the circle of lights. Eventually my Mother stopped watching the circle of light because she was a little scared so she didnt see where it went it what it did. Also aroung 4am I seen what looked like a giant star real low and kinda pulsating . I have a video camera but honestly am scared to go outside and record them.
Object Flight Path: Stationary,Hovering then path,Path with directional change
